      "title": "Best proximity point on different type contractions",
      "abstract": "In this manuscript, some proximity points are obtained by using different types cyclic contractions. Also, generalized cyclic Meir Keeler contraction is introduced and a new fixed point theorem for this cyclic mapping is stated."
